        <h5 class="mt-4">Step 2: Choose Your Theme</h5>
        <p>Visit the available theme demos:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Theme 1 (Classic):</strong> <code>/theme/1/</code></li>
          <li><strong>Theme 2 (Modern):</strong> <code>/theme/2/</code></li>
          <li><strong>Theme 3 (Premium):</strong> <code>/theme/3/</code></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4" id="project-structure">📂 Project Structure</h2>
        <p>Understanding the file organization will help you customize effectively:</p>
        <pre
          class="bg-body p-3 rounded"><code>src/
├── html/
│   ├── pages/              # Website pages
│   │   ├── theme/          # 3 theme variations
│   │   │   ├── 1/          # Classic theme
│   │   │   ├── 2/          # Modern theme
│   │   │   └── 3/          # Premium theme
│   │   └── index.astro     # Landing page
│   ├── layouts/            # Page layouts
│   │   ├── admin/          # Admin panel layout
│   │   └── front/          # Frontend layout
│   └── components/         # Reusable components
├── scss/                   # Styles (customize here)
│   ├── variables/          # Color & theme variables
│   ├── components/         # Component styles
│   └── style.scss          # Main stylesheet
├── js/                     # JavaScript functionality
├── assets/                 # Images, fonts, data
│   ├── img/               # Images & logos
│   ├── data/              # Sample data files
│   └── fonts/             # Custom fonts
└── utils/                  # Helper functions</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4" id="customization">🎨 Basic Customization</h2>

        <h5 class="mt-4">Changing Colors & Branding</h5>
        <p>Edit the main color variables in <code>src/scss/variables/_colors.scss</code>:</p>
        <pre
          class="bg-body p-3 rounded"><code>// Primary brand colors
$primary: #667eea;          // Your main color
$secondary: #764ba2;        // Secondary color
$success: #28a745;          // Success messages
$info: #17a2b8;             // Info messages</code></pre>

        <h5 class="mt-4">Updating Your Logo</h5>
        <p>Replace logo files in <code>src/assets/img/</code>:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><code>logo.png</code> - Main logo (recommended: 200x60px)</li>
          <li><code>logo-dark.png</code> - Dark theme variant</li>
          <li><code>favicon.ico</code> - Browser icon</li>
        </ul>

        <h5 class="mt-4">Editing Content</h5>
        <p>Most content can be found in:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Homepage:</strong> <code>src/html/pages/index.astro</code></li>
          <li><strong>Theme Pages:</strong> <code>src/html/pages/theme/[1-3]/</code></li>
          <li><strong>Sample Data:</strong> <code>src/assets/data/</code></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4" id="themes">🎭 Working with Themes</h2>
        <p>Each theme includes the same functionality with different visual styles:</p>

        <div class="row g-3">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h6 class="card-title">Theme 1: Classic</h6>
                <p class="card-text small">
                  Traditional design with professional styling, perfect for established communities.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h6 class="card-title">Theme 2: Modern</h6>
                <p class="card-text small">
                  Clean, contemporary design with vibrant colors and modern typography.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h6 class="card-title">Theme 3: Premium</h6>
                <p class="card-text small">
                  Sophisticated design with advanced animations and premium styling.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
          <i class="ri-lightbulb-line me-2"></i>
          <strong>Tip:</strong> Start with one theme, customize it to your needs, then apply those changes
          to other themes if needed.
        </div>
      </div>

